        <p>This decision was not easy, as we recognize the valuable skills and experience you bring to the table. We want to assure you that this outcome does not diminish your professional qualifications or potential.</p>


        <div class="highlight">
            <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>üí° We Value Your Interest:</strong></p>
