            <li>Visit our careers portal: [CAREERS_URL]</li>
            <li>Subscribe to job alerts for roles matching your profile</li>
        </ul>

        <p>We sincerely appreciate your time and interest in [COMPANY NAME]. We wish you every success in your job search and hope our paths may cross again in the future.</p>

        <p>Should you have any questions, please feel free to reach out to us at <strong>[HR_EMAIL]</strong>.</p>

        <div class="signature">
