            [Designation]<br>
            Talent Acquisition Department<br>
            [COMPANY NAME]</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 13px;">
            <strong>Email:</strong> [HR_EMAIL]<br>
            <strong>Phone:</strong> [HR_PHONE]<br>
            <strong>Website:</strong> [COMPANY_WEBSITE]
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an official communication from [COMPANY NAME].</p>
        <p><strong>Confidentiality Notice:</strong> This email and any attachments are confidential and intended solely for the addressee.</p>
    </div>
</body>
